sequenceDiagram
    participant DOM as Lista de Tarefas
    participant MO as MutationObserver
    participant G as Gerenciador

    DOM->>MO: childList mudou
    MO->>G: Callback com mutations
    G->>G: Conta addedNodes e removedNodes
    G->>G: Atualiza contador
    G->>DOM: Modifica contador
    Note over G,DOM: Flag evita loop infinito
